headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week on the Podium: The Dinka Veto Modern
content: The Diamond Casino & Resort is offering up a Dinka Veto Modern atop the podium this week. Give the Lucky Wheel a spin for the opportunity to ride off into the sunset on a gas-guzzling deathtrap that’s hardly street legal — or walk away with GTA$, RP, clothing, mystery prizes, and more.
